    to be able to use Trividia's blood glucose sensor and transmitter for measuring and monitoring blood glucose levels
    of diabetics (the "
Product
"). The Product in connection with the CGM APP assists diabetics
    in measuring, displaying and monitoring their current blood glucose levels, in identifying long-term glucose trends
    and developments based on their glucose levels, and warns diabetics if they become hyperglycemic or hypoglycemic and
    thus reach life-threatening states.
