    the relationship between any individual who registered a User Account for the use of the CGM APP (the "
User
") and Trividia. In the relationship between the user and Trividia, these T&Cs apply
    exclusively to the use of the CGM APP. The application of terms and conditions of the User is expressly rejected,
    even if the User expressly refers to their application.
